# Project overview

This is a Rails 7 API-only app that implements a Coinbase futures trading bot. It uses PostgreSQL for state and GoodJob for background processing.

- Rails: 7.2.x (API-only)
- Ruby: 3.2.4
- DB: PostgreSQL via `ENV['DATABASE_URL']`
- Jobs: Active Job with `:good_job` adapter, dashboard mounted at `/good_job` in development

Core services to implement:
- Market data subscriber (ingest and normalize Coinbase futures feeds)
- Signal generation (strategy logic)
- Execution (order placement, risk controls, kill switch)
- Reconciliation (positions, PnL, drift correction)

Operational concerns:
- Health checks at `/up`
- Metrics and observability (to be added)
- Safe rollout with branch protection and CI (RuboCop, Brakeman)
